data.description: Opportunity knocks! LOTS OF INCENTIVES FOR FIRST TIME HOME BUYERS OR SECOND TIME HOME BUYERS! SELLER MOTIVATED!! MOST IMPORTANT LOCATION! LOCATION! LOCATION! MAKE YOUR APPOINTMENT BEFORE IT'S GONE!!  This beautiful and well maintained 4 bed/2 bath home. Make this beautiful and cozy home yours today! Lots of upgrades worth more than $20k, some of the upgrades include laminate flooring and tile Flooring, backsplash on kitchen, newer fridge, newer stove, newer dishwasher, and more! This home has a lot to offer, you must see it to appreciate it. Country Wide Estate is the perfect community to call home with its beautiful Florida lifestyle. The best local restaurants and shopping are just a short drive away. Find everything you need in Davenport! Located just minutes from world class theme parks and attractions. Love the outdoors? Play a round at the many local golf courses or slow down the pace and explore nearby parks and farmer’s markets. Your home at Country Wide Estate will be in the center of it all! Make your appointment for viewing today!
